spec_data.Name: mdds-devel
spec_data.Description:
mdds is a collection of multi-dimensional data structures and
indexing algorithms.

It implements the following data structures:
* segment tree
* flat segment tree
* rectangle set
* point quad tree
* multi type matrix
* multi type vector

See README for a brief description of the structures.
